last_episode_to_air.name: The Wedding
last_episode_to_air.overview: An unanticipated job offer forces Sophia, Diamond and the rest of the family to pull together the big wedding in just 48 hours; but as soon as they're successful, Hollywood descends on Star Falls and threatens to ruin their family event!

name: Star Falls
overview: Teen Sophia persuades a Hollywood star, Bo Brooks, and his family to live in her house while he shoots a movie in town, hoping that he'll fall in love with her mom.

episodes.name: The Celebrity Setup
episodes.overview: When Sophia rescues the dog of Hollywood star Craig Brooks, she seizes the opportunity to set her mom up with him. When that doesn't work, she takes things a step further and has the star and his three kids move in with them!

episodes.name: The Everything Wash
episodes.overview: When Sophia sees that Diamond gets whatever she wants whenever she wants, she hopes for the same treatment from Beth. Instead, Craig sees the error in his ways and tells Diamond she has to earn her own money.

episodes.name: The Assistant
episodes.overview: When Craig's assistant quits, Sophia and Diamond get uber-competitive as they both vie for the job!

episodes.name: The Birthday
episodes.overview: Sophia promises not to tell anyone about Beth's usually low-key birthday. But when Diamond finds out, she plans a huge surprise party without telling Sophia.

episodes.name: The Owl Bomb
episodes.overview: When Diamond blames Star Falls for her drop in online followers, Sophia offers to help her make new videos for her channel. But the girls clash when Sophia prefers to focus on causes, while Diamond just wants to have fun.

episodes.name: The Play
episodes.overview: When Sophia tries to produce the best town play ever, she finds it hard to let go of her “control freak” nature and collaborate with others, especially when Nate casts Diamond in the lead role.

episodes.name: The Picnic Auction
episodes.overview: When Sophia wants to raise money to fix a damaged statue, Diamond suggests a Picnic Auction- that can include Craig! Sophia likes the idea but is concerned about Beth- until she totally denies having feelings for Craig.

episodes.name: The Mole
episodes.overview: When Diamond's private conversation is leaked to the tabloids, she's sure Sophia is responsible. Sophia is sure she's innocent, but when Diamond tries to teach her how to handle the media, Sophia grows increasingly paranoid!

episodes.name: The Co-Star
episodes.overview: When the girls find out Craig's new co-star might have designs on him, they have to get her out of the picture, and force Craig and Beth to admit their feelings for each other.

episodes.name: The Pet Whisperer
episodes.overview: Nate tries to help Sophia regain her confidence, which is shaken by Phoenix who helps at the rescue and proves to be a genuine pet whisperer.

episodes.name: The Red Carpet
episodes.overview: Diamond and Sophia convince Beth to go to a glitzy L.A. event with Craig after Phoenix convinces his father to ask her. Will this risky move finally get them to admit their romantic feelings or tank the relationship?

episodes.name: The Creth
episodes.overview: When new celebrity "it couple" Beth and Craig attract the paparazzi, Sophia and Beth's once-simple lives are turned upside down. Sophia is determined to rid Star Falls of the problem before it ruins her mom's new relationship.

episodes.name: The Fall of the Owl
episodes.overview: When Sophia, Diamond and Phoenix offer to take care of The Falling Owl Café while Ginger's away for the weekend, the kids each attempt to run things their own way – which results in the café being shut down!

episodes.name: The Engagement
episodes.overview: When Sophia and Diamond discover Craig is planning to propose to Beth that evening, they set out to ensure it's the best, most romantic proposal ever! Unfortunately absolutely nothing works out as planned.

episodes.name: The Boys vs the Girls
episodes.overview: When the boys are forced to temporarily stay at the main house, the girls lay down some ground rules. But when the boys refuse to oblige and make rules of their own, a battle erupts for control!

episodes.name: The Camping Trip
episodes.overview: Craig and Diamond are excited to tag along on Sophia and Beth's annual camping trip. But when Diamond feels completely out of her element in the outdoors, she ends up going overboard to prove she can be a super wilderness girl!

episodes.name: The Mystery Artist
episodes.overview: When Phoenix discovers an exciting new artist is in Star Falls, he designs a unique installation to capture their attention. His time and focus are stretched to the limit when the parents go away and put him in charge.

episodes.name: The Family Picnic
episodes.overview: When it's time for the annual Star Falls Family Picnic, Sophia and Beth are excited to compete as the Miller-Brooks. With the help of Craig and Diamond they hope to finally beat their picnic nemesis- the King Family!

episodes.name: The Standing and the Dresses
episodes.overview: Phoenix and Bo plan a boys' day with Craig, but their plans are ruined when Craig's trailer is towed out of town- with him inside it! Meanwhile, the girls take Beth wedding dress shopping.

episodes.name: The Wedding
episodes.overview: An unanticipated job offer forces Sophia, Diamond and the rest of the family to pull together the big wedding in just 48 hours; but as soon as they're successful, Hollywood descends on Star Falls and threatens to ruin their family event!
